WEBVTT

00:00,000 --> 00:04,950
Why this post matters

00:05,000 --> 00:09,950
The strongest idea in Decision quality loop for weekly execution is simple: improve decisions where work actually happens.

00:10,000 --> 00:14,950
Test one manager cue for two cycles, then keep only what shifts behavior.

00:15,000 --> 00:19,950
Use a compact loop: signal, decision, action, and evidence review each week.

00:20,000 --> 00:24,950
That structure raises first-pass quality and cuts repeated errors within two weeks.

00:25,000 --> 00:29,950
Pick one decision ritual today and convert it into a measurable operating habit.
